			<div class="content" id="post-content-1680960">
									

<p>There is no proof that the shadows are anything but, well, shadows. Yet the Foundation has put forth plans and means for its destruction. I'm not an expert on holes between worlds, but it occurs to me that if such a hole was to be opened (which seems to be the implied fear), destroying the gateway may just mean you now have a(nother) hole into another world you can't close. If everything doesn't explode. Downvoted.</p>

